    "updated_at": "2017-03-21T21:58:09Z",
    "body": "Funnily enough I just had the very same issue in chrome itself as well when the chrome process is closed and then you open as the very first (and only) tab a scrollable page. Resizing the window fixed it.\r\n\r\nFor example, just close the chrome process and then on a command line do \"```start https://github.com/electron/electron/issues/8960#issuecomment-288228600```\"."
